title: The Jboy Show - Can Miami compete against Alabama with David Pollack
itunes:title: The Jboy Show - Can Miami compete against Alabama with David Pollack
description:
Jake and the boys preview Miami vs Alabama (3:00), Stewart Mandel joins us to take a look at the future of college football (18:00), Jake gives his top 5 SEC players of the last 20 years (32:00) and David Pollack joins us to break down Georgia's week 1 matchup with Clemson (40:00) Make sure to check us out LIVE on Youtube every day at 3pm EST, plus follow us @thejboyshow on all social media platforms!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
